import React, { useDeferredValue, useEffect, useRef, useState } from 'react'; import { ChartDummyData } from 'utils/mockData'; function RechartLayer({ salaryList }) { const ref = useRef(); const [mouseXState, setMouseX] = useState(0); const [mouseYState, setMouseY] = useState(0); const [career, setCareer] = useState(0); const [salary, setSalary] = useState(0); const [visibleState, setVisible] = useState(false); const mouseX = useDeferredValue(mouseXState); const mouseY = useDeferredValue(mouseYState); const visible = useDeferredValue(visibleState); const [gridHeight, setGridHeight] = useState([]); const handleMoveMouse = (e) => { if ( e.clientX - ref.current.getBoundingClientRect().x < 45 || e.clientX - ref.current.getBoundingClientRect().x > 760 || e.clientY > 370 ) { setVisible(false); return; } setVisible(true); if (e.clientX - ref.current.getBoundingClientRect().x > 710) { setMouseX(670); } else { setMouseX( Math.floor( (e.clientX - ref.current.getBoundingClientRect().x + 33) / 67, ) * 67 + 20, ); } setMouseY(e.clientY - ref.current.getBoundingClientRect().y); }; useEffect(() => { switch (mouseX) { case 87: setCareer(0); setSalary(salaryList[0].salary); break; case 154: setCareer(1); setSalary(salaryList[1].salary); break; case 221: setCareer(2); setSalary(salaryList[2].salary); break; case 288: setCareer(3); setSalary(salaryList[3].salary); break; case 355: setCareer(4); setSalary(salaryList[4].salary); break; case 422: setCareer(5); setSalary(salaryList[5].salary); break; case 489: setCareer(6); setSalary(salaryList[6].salary); break; case 556: setCareer(7); setSalary(salaryList[7].salary); break; case 623: setCareer(8); setSalary(salaryList[8].salary); break; case 690: setCareer(9); setSalary(salaryList[9].salary); break; case 757: setCareer(10); setSalary(salaryList[10].salary); break; default: break; } }, [mouseX]); useEffect(() => { if (salaryList.length === 0) { return; } let temp = []; for (let i = 0; i <= Math.round(salaryList[10].salary / 1000); i += 1) { temp = [ ...temp, (i * 352) / Math.round(salaryList[10].salary / 1000) + 5, ]; } setGridHeight(temp); }, [salaryList]); console.log(gridHeight); return ( <> {visible && (

{career === 0 ? '신입' : `${career}년`}

{salary} 만원

)} ); } export default RechartLayer;
